author: AP
title: Hockey field to hospital ward; Lynch's life amid pandemic
description: The coronavirus pandemic has ended any chance Rachael Lynch had of competing for Olympic gold in Tokyo this year
content:
PERTH, Australia (AP) — The coronavirus pandemic ended any chance of Rachael Lynch competing for Olympic gold in Tokyo this year. Now she’s switching into the medical mode to take on the virus.
